12:53.258 --> 12:55.634
Kept one of their menus
last time we were here.

12:59.055 --> 13:00.889
You said order.

13:01.808 --> 13:03.726
I meant order food.

13:04.894 --> 13:06.437
Where is Robbie?

13:06.521 --> 13:08.981
- He went out.
- Out where?

13:09.065 --> 13:12.484
I don't know.
He just took your car and left.

13:12.610 --> 13:15.029
Who said that? Who's there?

13:15.113 --> 13:16.947
It's the clam burglar.

13:44.893 --> 13:46.268
Steven, look at this.

13:46.352 --> 13:48.771
- What's up?
- Check it out!

13:52.400 --> 13:55.110
You ever see something like that?

13:55.195 --> 13:57.821
Springtime, maybe.
Not this time of year.

13:57.906 --> 14:01.116
Come on, we can see better
from the back yard.

14:22.722 --> 14:24.890
You got to come see this!

14:36.027 --> 14:38.821
- That is so weird.
