16:11.748 --> 16:12.998
Shit!

16:18.546 --> 16:20.255
Where's Robbie?

16:21.758 --> 16:23.258
I don't know.

16:24.636 --> 16:26.595
Is Robbie okay?

16:28.765 --> 16:30.682
Are you okay?

16:30.767 --> 16:32.726
Where's the thunder?

16:33.228 --> 16:34.937
Why won't it stop?

16:49.118 --> 16:50.744
Is it over?

17:06.094 --> 17:07.426
Where are you going?

17:07.512 --> 17:11.640
Just... I'm just checking things out.
Just wait. Wait there.

17:11.723 --> 17:14.434
- Are we gonna be okay?
- I don't know.

17:14.519 --> 17:16.686
- You don't know?
- No, I meant, I just...

17:16.771 --> 17:18.521
Rachel, please.

17:18.606 --> 17:21.983
Just stop asking so many questions.
Just wait here.

17:59.856 --> 18:02.149
Turn everything off.

