18:09.532 --> 18:12.492
You believe this, Ray? Every single car.

18:14.412 --> 18:16.413
Jesus. Jesus, Jesus, Jesus.

18:16.497 --> 18:18.206
- The car just stopped, and...
- You're okay?

18:18.291 --> 18:20.042
- Are you okay? You all right?
- The lightning started to hit

18:20.126 --> 18:21.460
about a block away,
over and over again.

18:21.544 --> 18:23.587
