18:33.056 --> 18:34.056
- I don't know.
- Twenty-six times?

18:34.140 --> 18:35.599
- Yeah.
- Okay.

18:36.392 --> 18:37.809
- You're okay?
- Yeah.

18:37.894 --> 18:39.936
Good. All right, well,
your sister is in the house,

18:40.021 --> 18:43.357
