Hey, move. You feel that?

20:51.694 --> 20:54.821
- I feel that.
- Hey, Bobby, come check this out.

20:55.281 --> 20:56.656
- You feel that?
- Feel that?

20:56.741 --> 20:58.533
- Yeah, I feel that.
