20:58.618 --> 21:00.952
- There's no subway here.
- F train, maybe?

21:01.037 --> 21:02.454
That can't be the water main.

21:02.538 --> 21:03.872
There's nothing else down there.

21:03.956 --> 21:05.624
- Water main doesn't run through here.
- Feel that?

21:05.708 --> 21:07.542
Well, there's something down there
and it's moving.

21:12.757 --> 21:15.091
Everybody, move back.

21:15.426 --> 21:17.385
Whoa. Back it up. Come on.

21:18.221 --> 21:19.554
Let's go.

21:20.389 --> 21:23.016
Come on, folks. Back up. Get back.

21:30.733 --> 21:33.693
Help me out here. Get back.

21:38.491 --> 21:40.242
- Go! Move!
- Everybody, get out of the way!

21:40.326 --> 21:43.203
Everyone, back up!
Everyone, clear the intersection!

21:43.287 --> 21:47.374
Get out of the way! Back up! Back up!
Get out of the way!

22:04.183 --> 22:08.228
- Forget it! Get back!
- Get the hell out of the street!

22:19.907 --> 22:21.575
Move away!

22:22.493 --> 22:25.287
Come on,
we've got to clear this area now!

23:15.755 --> 23:17.505
That's my car!

23:20.009 --> 23:21.426
Go, go.

23:21.510 --> 23:23.678
Get the hell out of here!

23:47.912 --> 23:49.829
Oh, my God!

23:50.873 --> 23:52.040
Come on, people! Let's go!

23:52.124 --> 23:53.875
Come on, back up!

23:53.959 --> 23:56.544
Please! Move back!

25:18.961 --> 25:20.462
Watch it!

25:22.965 --> 25:24.799
Oh, my God.

25:26.260 --> 25:28.470
Ray, no. Stay, man.

25:37.354 --> 25:39.105
Just stay.

25:39.648 --> 25:43.485
- Just stay back here. Stay back!
