What happened?

28:18.891 --> 28:20.600
What's going on?

28:21.602 --> 28:23.478
Dad, what's the matter?

28:24.647 --> 28:26.814
What's all that stuff all over you?

28:30.527 --> 28:32.236
- Ray.
- What's all this stuff?

28:32.321 --> 28:33.696
Hello?

28:34.448 --> 28:35.907
Ray?

29:09.942 --> 29:12.276
We're leaving this house in 60 seconds.

29:12.361 --> 29:13.611
What? Why?
