54:33.130 --> 54:34.714
Put it down.

54:39.762 --> 54:41.387
Dad!

54:43.224 --> 54:44.974
Okay, man, now, listen.

54:45.142 --> 54:48.186
- Put down the gun. I'm taking the car.
- My daughter's in the car.

54:48.270 --> 54:50.396
- Put down the gun. I'm taking the car.
- Please. All I want...

54:50.481 --> 54:53.149
- Put down the goddamn gun!
- All I want is my daughter.

54:53.234 --> 54:55.777
- I'm taking the car, man.
- Please, I just want my daughter.

54:55.861 --> 54:57.820
Please, let me...
Let me just take my daughter. Can I...

54:57.905 --> 54:59.447
- All I want is my daughter.
- Yeah, yeah, yeah.

54:59.532 --> 55:00.782
- Go ahead, man. Take her.
- Take my daughter?

55:00.866 --> 55:01.824
Take her. Yeah. Yeah.

55:01.909 --> 55:03.535
Robbie.

55:12.962 --> 55:14.754
Take me with you.

56:16.358 --> 56:18.401
Have you seen this girl?
This is my daughter.

56:18.485 --> 56:21.237
He needs his medicine.

56:32.166 --> 56:34.083
We've got it the worst,
that's what I heard.

56:34.168 --> 56:37.253
The US, mostly.
South America and Asia, some.

56:37.338 --> 56:39.047
There's nothing going on in Europe.

56:39.131 --> 56:41.841
Europe got the worst of it,
that's what everybody's saying.

56:41.925 --> 56:44.427
- Completely wiped out some of it.
- I don't give a shit who it is.

56:44.511 --> 56:46.971
I got up close to one of those things
in Stanfordville.

56:47.056 --> 56:48.931
If they're all over the place, we're dead.

56:49.016 --> 56:51.893
- Looks like the power's still on here.
- Yeah.

56:51.977 --> 56:54.020
Yeah, power's still on.

56:54.188 --> 56:57.106
Because nothing bad's come up
from the ground.

56:57.191 --> 57:00.526
- Hold on. Hold on, move back.
- Watch out there, lady.

57:01.028 --> 57:03.029
I said, move back.

57:39.483 --> 57:43.778
unless you are O-positive
and Rh-negative, thank you very much,

57:43.862 --> 57:46.864
but we already have
more blood than we can use.

57:46.949 --> 57:50.451
