58:17.688 --> 58:19.981
Ray! Ray! Ray!

58:20.065 --> 58:22.525
- Sheryl?
- Yeah. Hey.

58:22.609 --> 58:24.318
Oh, my gosh, is this your...

58:24.403 --> 58:25.737
- Are these your kids?
- This is Rachel.

58:25.821 --> 58:28.531
Hi, I'm Sheryl. How are you?
