58:57.728 --> 58:59.729
You're gonna have to give us
a few minutes.

58:59.813 --> 59:02.774
But don't worry,
there'll be plenty of room for everybody.

59:03.358 --> 59:06.319
- We got sick people here. Let us on.
- Let us on, for Christ's sake.

59:40.187 --> 59:44.065
Cast off. Get that ramp up.

